🛠️ Requirements

🔴 Required Tools

sudo apt install nmap curl sqlmap nikto gobuster hydra dnsutils netcat-traditional whatweb -y

🟡 Optional Tools

sudo apt install wpscan masscan sslscan -y

pip install wafw00f --break-system-packages

⚡ Installation

git clone https://github.com/your-username/phantom-analyst.git

cd phantom-analyst

chmod +x phantom.py

▶️ Usage

🔹 Basic Scan

python3 phantom.py -t <target>

🔹 With Reverse Shell Listener

python3 phantom.py -t <target> --shell
🔹 Custom Shell Port

python3 phantom.py -t <target> --shell --shell-port 5555

🔹 Skip Dependency Check

python3 phantom.py -t <target> --no-dep-check

📁 Output

Reports are saved in:

~/phantom_reports/

Generated Files

📄 phantom_<timestamp>.md → Human-readable report

📊 phantom_<timestamp>.json → Structured data

